    "To thoroughly evaluate the effective-ness of our proposed agent framework under zero-shot con-ditions, we conduct experiments on three widely adoptedvisual grounding benchmarks: RefCOCO (Yu et al. 2016),RefCOCO+ (Yu et al.",
